### **4. 37_StreamPlotEngine**  
**Description:**  
A real-time plotting utility for live numeric streams.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# StreamPlotEngine - Live Graph Plotting Tool

StreamPlotEngine turns any stream of numbers into a dynamic, auto-scrolling chart using Matplotlib.

## Features
- Real-time updates  
- Minimal and clean UI  
- Adjustable frame rate  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/37_StreamPlotEngine.git
cd 37_StreamPlotEngine
python visualize.py
